==English==

===Pronunciation===
*IPA: /sp å…™Ààn…õs…ônt/ SAMPA: /spVI'nEs@nt/

===Adjective===
'''spinescent'''
# Having a spine or spines.
# Terminating in a spine.

====Usage notes====
This does not refer to spine in the sense of a backbone or book binding, but in the sense of "spiny". Cacti and sea urchins are spinescent.

